PrecisAmendments (Phase I) to the OCEAN DUMPING REGULATIONS, 1988 which replace the existing five permit application forms with one revised general form (which will improve application information and request it in a more practical and usable format) and replace the current fee scale of $50 to $1,000 with a flat rate fee of $2,500, effective September 30, 1993.
